#### **Pattern D: Event Decorators with Lifecycle Binding**

```
Event.debounce/throttle/buffer(sourceEvent, disposable?)
    ↓
    creates new Emitter<T>
    ↓
    Emitter constructor calls onWillAddFirstListener → subscribe to source
    ↓
    when last listener removed → onDidRemoveLastListener → unsubscribe
    ↓
    if disposable provided: add(emitter) for cleanup
```

#### **Pattern E: Queuing with Cancellation**

```
Throttler/Delayer/ResourceQueue
    ↓
    uses CancellationTokenSource internally
    ↓
    passes token to queued tasks
    ↓
    dispose() cancels source
    ↓
    tasks can check token.isCancellationRequested
